    <div class="whoweare">
        <h1>Who We Are</h1>
        <p class="glass">
            Welcome to BIBTour, where every journey is an adventure waiting to be
            unfolded. As passionate travel enthusiasts, we believe that exploration
            is not just a destination; it's a lifestyle. At BIBTour, we curate
            extraordinary travel experiences that go beyond the ordinary, offering
            you the chance to discover the world in a way that stays with you
            forever.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="whychooseheader">
        <h2>Why Choose BIBTour?</h2>
        <h3 data-text="Unforgettable Destinations">Unforgettable Destinations</h3>
        <p>
            From the sun-kissed beaches to the snow-capped mountains, BIBTour takes
            you to the most breathtaking destinations around the globe. Whether you
            seek cultural immersion, natural wonders, or thrilling adventures, we
            have the perfect itinerary for you.
        </p>
        <h3 data-text="Tailored Experiences">Tailored Experiences</h3>
        <p>
            We understand that every traveler is unique. That's why our team crafts
            personalized itineraries to cater to your preferences and interests.
            Your journey with BIBTour is not just a vacation; it's a tailor-made
            experience designed exclusively for you.
        </p>
        <h3 data-text="Comfort and Quality">Comfort and Quality</h3>
        <p>
            We prioritize your comfort and satisfaction. Our carefully selected
            accommodations, transportation, and tour guides ensure that you
            experience the highest quality throughout your trip. Relax and enjoy the
            journey while we take care of the details.
        </p>
        <h3 data-text="Passionate Team">Passionate Team</h3>
        <p>
            Our team is driven by a shared love for travel. We are dedicated to
            providing you with exceptional service, making every moment of your trip
            special. From planning to execution, we are committed to exceeding your
            expectations.
        </p>
    </div>
